<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1322902' id='t-1322902'>but apparently they go
all around the buses and the trucks</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1325664' id='t-1325664'>and it's crazy and it's noisy
and it's exciting.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1328506' id='t-1328506'>He figured that this
would drive up the dopamine,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1330816' id='t-1330816'>and she'd fall in love with him.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1332372' id='t-1332372'>So off they go and she's squealing
and squeezing him</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1337370' id='t-1337370'>and laughing and having a wonderful time.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1339911' id='t-1339911'>An hour later they get down
off of the rickshaw,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1343474' id='t-1343474'>and she throws her hands up and she says,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1347078' id='t-1347078'>&quot;Wasn't that wonderful?&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1349414' id='t-1349414'>And, &quot;Wasn't that rickshaw
driver handsome!&quot;</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
