</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
22:53
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1362000' id='t-1362000'>There's magic to love!</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
22:54
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1363186' id='t-1363186'>(Applause)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
22:55
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1364821' id='t-1364821'>But I will end by saying
that millions of years ago,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1368465' id='t-1368465'>we evolved three basic drives:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1370821' id='t-1370821'>the sex drive, romantic love</span>
